<title>
Rear End Door Window Defogger System Description
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Rear end door window defogger system consists of rear defogger (1), rear defogger switch (2), rear defogger relay (4) and BCM (5).
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
BCM judges rear defogger switch condition when rear defogger relay turns on with engine running, thereby causing rear defogger to operate. After a certain period of time, BCM turns off relay to discontinue operation of rear defogger.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
